NUT\-Monitor\-py2gtk2
is an implementation that relies on a Python 2\&.x interpreter (tested with 2\&.6 or 2\&.7 generation) and GTK2 UI library;
.RE
.sp
.RS 4
.ie n \{\
\h'-04'\(bu\h'+03'\c
